Ing '''Dimane''' ([[Arabu]]: الديمان) metung yang mabunduk a bariu king labuad nang Pangulu (Northern region) ning [[Lebanon]], king [[Bsharri District|Distritu ning Bsharri]]. Maki katas yang manga 1400 m babo ning dayatmalat/dagat.

Magsilbi yang tuknangan a pangkaleldo (summer residence) ning Patriarkang Catolicung [[Maronite]] (Maronite Catholic Patriarch), a king salukuyan i  [[Cardinal Mar Nasrallah Boutros Sfeir]] ing Dimane. Mikutkut ya ing batung pundasiun (foundation stone) ning tuknangan ning patriarka ketang Setiembre 28, 1899.

Kilala ya murin ing Dimane ketang "Mula da reng Patriarka" (Garden of the Patriarchs), a atyu king albugan nang gilid (western side) ning balen, ampo ketang misnang katuang gasgas (ancient footpath) a magumpisa king gulut ning pisamban ning parokia, at papunta king lalam ning [[Lambak ning Kadish]] (Kadish Valley).

